{"data":[{"date":"23:43 07/08","title":"HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i ch\u1ec9 ra c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 hay nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 1-1 Uzbekistan","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/4/6/hlv-le-thuy-hai-khen-ngoi-1-cau-thu-sau-tran-u23-viet-nam-11-uzbekistan.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb sau khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Uzbekistan, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1ec1 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i khen ng\u1ee3i \u0110\u1ee9c Huy sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a\u00a0U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 7/8, \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf c\u00fap Vinaphone 2018 g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 duy\u00ean n\u1ee3 Uzbekistan.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c uy hi\u1ebfp khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng trong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn. Tuy nhi\u00ean \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, \u0110T U23 Uzbekistan c\u0169ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1ebb g\u00e3y c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ee3t l\u00ean b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau hi\u1ec7p 1 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf ph\u00fat 65 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. R\u1ea5t may Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1eabn k\u1ecbp t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a 1-1 chung cu\u1ed9c.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i khen ng\u1ee3i \u0110\u1ee9c Huysau tr\u1eadn U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i khen ng\u1ee3i \u0110\u1ee9c Huysau tr\u1eadn U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/HLV-Le-Thuy-Hai-khen-ngoi-Duc-Huysau-tran-U23-Viet-Nam-hinh-anh.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110\u1ee9c Huy \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i khen ng\u1ee3i \u1edf tr\u1eadn U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 1-1 U23 Uzbekistan</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng n\u00e0y, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i n\u00f3i v\u1edbi Tri th\u1ee9c tr\u1ebb: \"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t r\u1ed3i nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng h\u01a1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea1n. Ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u00e2y m\u1edbi l\u00e0 thu\u1ed1c th\u1eed li\u1ec1u cao c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng Park. H\u00f4m nay v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t kh\u00ed h\u1eadu h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 quen r\u1ed3i. Th\u1ee9 2, h\u1ecd ch\u01a1i b\u1eb1ng s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh, c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u00e1p s\u00e1t nhanh, d\u00f9ng s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean l\u00e0m ch\u00fang ta b\u1ecb kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng. Th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t r\u00f5.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1ecd c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng, b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh l\u00f9i s\u00e2u, khi ch\u00fang ta c\u00f3 b\u00f3ng l\u00e0 h\u1ecd ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng l\u1ecfng l\u1ebbo. Ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta th\u1ef1c ra kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m nh\u01b0ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ch\u01b0a c\u00f3, c\u00f3 th\u00ec ch\u01b0a gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1\u201d.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/tin-moi-nhat-ve-chan-thuong-cua-quang-hai-168-193974.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/tin-moi-nhat-ve-chan-thuong-cua-quang-hai.png\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/tin-moi-nhat-ve-chan-thuong-cua-quang-hai-168-193974.html\">Tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Quang H\u1ea3i</span><br />\r\nChia s\u1ebb trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 cung c\u1ea5p nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin ban \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n Quang H\u1ea3i trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-u23-uzbekistan-noi-gi-sau-tran-hoa-truoc-u23-viet-nam-168-193970.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/hlv-u23-uzbekistan-noi-gi-sau-tran-hoa-truoc-u23-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-u23-uzbekistan-noi-gi-sau-tran-hoa-truoc-u23-viet-nam-168-193970.html\">HLV U23 Uzbekistan n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a tr\u01b0\u1edbc U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam?</span><br />\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV U23 Uzbekistan, Nuraliev Dilshod \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng cho r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e1nh r\u01a1i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00ec s\u1ef1 ch\u1ee7 quan \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-phat-bieu-292-193972.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/hlv-park-hang-seo-phat-bieu.JPG\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-phat-bieu-292-193972.html\">V\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu, HLV Park Hang Seo lo \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u1ee7 quan</span><br />\r\nGi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng, HLV Park Hang Seo v\u1eabn lo l\u1eafng khi g\u1eedi l\u1eddi nh\u1eafc r\u1eb1ng \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng ASIAD...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-uzbekistan-168-193967.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-uzbekistan.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-uzbekistan-168-193967.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 1-1 U23 Uzbekistan</span><br />\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh, th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 ch\u1ecbu kh\u00f3 di chuy\u1ec3n, U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Uzbekistan. V\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n r\u00fat ra...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nong-hlv-park-hang-seo-tao-bat-ngo-lon-tai-danh-sach-chinh-thuc-olympic-viet-nam-168-193960.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/nong-hlv-park-hang-seo-tao-bat-ngo-lon-tai-danh-sach-chinh-thuc-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nong-hlv-park-hang-seo-tao-bat-ngo-lon-tai-danh-sach-chinh-thuc-olympic-viet-nam-168-193960.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: HLV Park Hang Seo lo\u1ea1i V\u0103n L\u00e2m kh\u1ecfi danh s\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br />\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi U23 Uzbekistan, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ed1t danh s\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng H\u1ea3i \u2018l\u01a1\u2019 c\u0169ng t\u1ecf ra \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi \u0110\u1ee9c Huy, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 pha chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng m\u1eabu m\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201c\u0110\u1ee9c Huy l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ecb tr\u00ed, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 bi\u00ean, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 m\u00e0 v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1t. H\u00f4m nay c\u1eadu \u1ea5y chuy\u1ec1n r\u1ea5t hay. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9ng, to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed quan tr\u1ecdng v\u00ec ch\u1ec9 \u0111i c\u00f3 20 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00f4i. V\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0o v\u1eafng th\u00ec ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u1ea5p v\u00e0o. \u0110\u1ee9c Huy l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u1ea5y. Em \u1ea5y r\u1ea5t x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng di ASIAD\", \u00f4ng H\u1ea3i n\u00f3i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng cho r\u1eb1ng tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng quy\u1ebft th\u1eafng, b\u1eb1ng ch\u1ee9ng l\u00e0 HLV Park Hang Seo li\u00ean t\u1ee5c thay ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, v\u1ecb n\u00e0y c\u0169ng nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, c\u00e1c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 nhanh v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng H\u1ea3i \u2018l\u01a1\u2019 c\u0169ng t\u1ecf ra lo ng\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u00e1p \u0111\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ngang c\u01a1 nh\u01b0 Palestine. V\u1ecb c\u1ef1u gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt CLB B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00ec v\u1eady c\u0169ng cho r\u1eb1ng th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng \u00a0\u1edf ASIAD s\u1eafp t\u1edbi c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Highlight U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 1-1 U23 Uzbekistan<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">\t</span></strong></p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/7/Highlight-U23-Viet-Nam-vs-U23-Uzbekistan.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2113","checkdouble":"193977"},{"date":"00:09 08/08","title":"\u201cTi\u1ebfn D\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n t\u1ed1t\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/5/tien-dung-khong-bang-van-lam-nhung-cung-la-thu-mon-tot.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i cho r\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c lo\u1ea1i th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m l\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 t\u00ednh to\u00e1n c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng Park Hang Seo.</h2><h2>HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i so s\u00e1nh B\u00f9i\u00a0Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng v\u1edbi \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi k\u1ebft th\u00fac gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf 2018 v\u1edbi ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 danh s\u00e1ch tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc l\u00e0 \u1edf danh s\u00e1ch 20 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 1 \u1edf \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam hi\u1ec7n nay.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n t\u1ed1t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n t\u1ed1t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/Tien-Dung-khong-bang-Dang-Van-Lam-nhung-cung-la-thu-mon-tot-hinh-anh.JPG\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n V\u0103n L\u00e2m chia tay Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c V\u0103n L\u00e2m b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hi\u1ec3u l\u00e0 do m\u1ed7i \u0111\u1ed9i Olympic ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 sung 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i 23, v\u00e0 th\u1ea7y Park \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u01b0u ti\u00ean su\u1ea5t n\u00e0y cho V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft, Anh \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i cho bi\u1ebft: \"\u00d4ng \u1ea5y ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p mang 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi, mang L\u00e2m th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 mang H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng. Khi g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1 \u00e1p \u0111\u1eb7t th\u00ec c\u00f3 D\u0169ng t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n. \u0110i\u1ec1u g\u00ec c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n h\u1ebft nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 m\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecdn. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7n nh\u00ecn c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ednh to\u00e1n. G\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ea1nh th\u00ec H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft. N\u00f3i chung ph\u1ea3i l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn l\u00e0m sao cho ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt. C\u00f2n \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ecdn chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt h\u1ee3p l\u00fd th\u00ec c\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 h\u1ebft \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 ra con ng\u01b0\u1eddi. HLV n\u00e0o c\u0169ng th\u1ebf\".</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng H\u1ea3i \"l\u01a1\" c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1ec1 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a hai th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng v\u00e0 \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m.\u00a0Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 \u0110\u00f4ng cho bi\u1ebft: \"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u00f3 t\u1ed1t kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ee9. \u0110\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0o g\u1ea7n qu\u00e1 th\u00ec th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u00e0o c\u0169ng thua.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta v\u00e0o nhanh qu\u00e1 nh\u01b0 h\u00f4m nay thua l\u00e0 b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng. D\u0169ng l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00edch, \u00f4ng Park c\u0169ng bi\u1ebft th\u1ebf. V\u00e0 em \u1ea5y c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 k\u00e9m d\u00f9 b\u1eaft \u00edt \u1edf V-League. V\u00ec th\u1ebf \u00f4ng \u1ea5y c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc\".<br />\r\n<strong>Highlight U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Uzbekistan</strong></p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/7/Highlight-U23-Viet-Nam-vs-U23-Uzbekistan.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-le-thuy-hai-khen-ngoi-1-cau-thu-sau-tran-u23-viet-nam-11-uzbekistan-168-193977.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/4/6/hlv-le-thuy-hai-khen-ngoi-1-cau-thu-sau-tran-u23-viet-nam-11-uzbekistan.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-le-thuy-hai-khen-ngoi-1-cau-thu-sau-tran-u23-viet-nam-11-uzbekistan-168-193977.html\">HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i ch\u1ec9 ra c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 hay nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 1-1 Uzbekistan</span><br />\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Uzbekistan, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1ec1 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/tin-moi-nhat-ve-chan-thuong-cua-quang-hai-168-193974.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/tin-moi-nhat-ve-chan-thuong-cua-quang-hai.png\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/tin-moi-nhat-ve-chan-thuong-cua-quang-hai-168-193974.html\">Tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Quang H\u1ea3i</span><br />\r\nChia s\u1ebb trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 cung c\u1ea5p nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin ban \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n Quang H\u1ea3i trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-phat-bieu-292-193972.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/hlv-park-hang-seo-phat-bieu.JPG\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-phat-bieu-292-193972.html\">V\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu, HLV Park Hang Seo lo \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u1ee7 quan</span><br />\r\nGi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng, HLV Park Hang Seo v\u1eabn lo l\u1eafng khi g\u1eedi l\u1eddi nh\u1eafc r\u1eb1ng \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng ASIAD...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-uzbekistan-168-193967.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-uzbekistan.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-uzbekistan-168-193967.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 1-1 U23 Uzbekistan</span><br />\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh, th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 ch\u1ecbu kh\u00f3 di chuy\u1ec3n, U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Uzbekistan. V\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n r\u00fat ra...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p>\r\n<h1>\u00a0</h1></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2112","checkdouble":"193978"},{"date":"00:44 08/08","title":"\u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi b\u1ecb g\u1ea1ch t\u00ean kh\u1ecfi \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/8/dang-van-lam-noi-gi-sau-khi-bi-gach-ten-khoi-dt-olympic-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd chi 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Kepa Arrizabalaga. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n b\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n tr\u1ebb n\u00e0y v\u1edbi Athletic Bilbao.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea kh\u00e1t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nghi ng\u1edd g\u00ec v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c Thibaut Courtois mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi b\u1ecf Chelsea v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1eddi m\u1eddi ch\u00e0o t\u1eeb Real Madrid, tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 ra \u0111i. T\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Chelsea \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd v\u1edbi Real b\u1ea5t th\u00e0nh, anh s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng bi\u1ec7n ph\u00e1p c\u1ee9ng r\u1eafn h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, \u0111\u00e3 2 ng\u00e0y tr\u00f4i qua k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb h\u1ea1n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n, Courtois v\u1eabn b\u1eb7t v\u00f4 \u00e2m t\u00edn. K\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m r\u00f5 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a HLV Maurizio Sarri c\u0169ng b\u1ecb h\u1ee7y b\u1ecf. Th\u00f4ng qua \u0111\u00f3, Courtois g\u1eedi \u0111i th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n mu\u1ed1n t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00eam b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 l\u1ea7n n\u00e0o cho Chelsea.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd chi 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Kepa Arrizabalaga h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd chi 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Kepa Arrizabalaga h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/15/Chelsea-dong-y-chi-71-trieu-bang-mua-Kepa-Arrizabalaga-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Courtois kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n thi\u1ebft tha \u1edf l\u1ea1i Real</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nChelsea \u0111\u00e3 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u Courtois b\u1eaft bu\u1ed9c ra tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m r\u00f5 v\u1ee5 vi\u1ec7c. H\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n duy tr\u00ec k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt trong \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng dung t\u00fang h\u00e0nh vi n\u00e0y. Song song v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, The Blues c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ea9y nhanh qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh t\u00ecm th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nCh\u1ed1t mua Kepa</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo th\u00f4ng tin m\u00e0 t\u1edd Telegraph m\u1edbi \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i, Chelsea \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd chi 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Kepa Arrizabalaga c\u1ee7a Athletic Bilbao. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Bilbao tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb n\u00e0o cho th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y 24 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi The Blues bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a anh n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfp di\u1ec5n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kepa Arrizabalaga\" title=\"Kepa Arrizabalaga\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/29/chelsea-dong-y-chi-71-trieu-bang-mua-kepa-arrizabalaga.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Chelsea \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd chi 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Kepa Arrizabalaga</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i n\u00e0y cho th\u1ea5y Chelsea s\u1eafp ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a CLB ch\u1ec9 sau 1 n\u0103m khi \u0111\u01b0a Alvaro Morata v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb Real Madrid v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 tr\u1ea3 ngay 58 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u0103ng l\u00ean 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u00f9y th\u00e0nh t\u00edch. N\u00f3 c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0a Kepa tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y 1 th\u00e1ng sau khi Liverpool chi 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Alisson t\u1eeb Roma.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u00fac n\u00e0y, Chelsea \u0111ang ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n c\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u1edbi Kepa. Song song v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng k\u1ef3 k\u00e8o Real gia t\u0103ng th\u00eam s\u1ee9c n\u1eb7ng trong \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb mua Courtois. Los Blancos ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n chi 31 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng (35 tri\u1ec7u Euro) trong khi CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n nh\u1eadn v\u1ec1 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/sevilla-muon-co-batshuayi-180-193959.html\">\u201cBom x\u1ecbt\u201d Chelsea s\u1eafp chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi La Liga thi \u0111\u1ea5u</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-muon-muon-kovacic-172-193958.html\">L\u1ed9 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ea7y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd c\u1ee7a Mateo Kovacic \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sao-chelsea-hy-vong-sarri-khong-kho-hieu-nhu-conte-172-193918.html\">Sao Chelsea hy v\u1ecdng Sarri kh\u00f4ng kh\u00f3 hi\u1ec3u nh\u01b0 Conte</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-cho-nantes-muon-matt-miazga-172-193916.html\">Sao tr\u1ebb Chelsea ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111em cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/barkley-phat-bieu-ve-tuong-lai-tai-chelsea-172-193912.html\">\u201cSao x\u1ecbt\u201d Chelsea hy v\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111\u1eddi d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Sarri</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2111","checkdouble":"193979"},{"date":"00:56 08/08","title":"Chuy\u00ean gia Vi\u1ec7t n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo tr\u01b0\u1edbc Uzbekistan?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/chuyen-gia-viet-noi-gi-ve-tran-hoa-cua-thay-tro-park-hang-seo-truoc-uzbekistan.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, chuy\u00ean gia b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Nguy\u1ec5n S\u1ef9 Hi\u1ec3n cho r\u1eb1ng U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u1ea7n r\u00fat kinh nghi\u1ec7m trong t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc U23 Uzbekistan.</h2><h2>Chuy\u00ean gia Nguy\u1ec5n S\u1ef9 Hi\u1ec3n n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u00ean gia Nguy\u1ec5n S\u1ef9 Hi\u1ec3n n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u00ean gia Nguy\u1ec5n S\u1ef9 Hi\u1ec3n n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/38693374-407003336372383-80023-8216-9368-1533647643_600x0.jpg\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam su\u00fdt b\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 hai tr\u01b0\u1edbc\u00a0Uzbekistan</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 7/8, \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Uzbekistan v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-1. N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, chuy\u00ean gia b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, \u00f4ng Nguy\u1ec5n S\u1ef9 Hi\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e3 cho bi\u1ebft: \u201cKh\u00f4ng n\u00f3i \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t b\u1ed5 \u00edch cho U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam\". <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\"T\u00f4i th\u1ea5y h\u00f4m nay \u0110\u1ee9c Huy \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 bi\u00ean, nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u00fang ta m\u1ea5t ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00ean b\u00f3ng, ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o l\u00fac \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, U23 Uzbekistan ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t khi ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c,d\u00f9 h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng r\u00f5 r\u1ec7t v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n h\u00f3a th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u BHL c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i r\u00fat kinh nghi\u1ec7m.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb c\u1ef1u HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u0169ng c\u00f3 l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i cho pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c. \u0110\u00e2y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft khi ng\u00f4i sao SLNA \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee1 b\u00f3ng b\u1eb1ng ch\u00e2n tr\u00e1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi t\u0103ng b\u00f3ng b\u1eb1ng ch\u00e2n ph\u1ea3i qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng \u0111i v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf c\u00fap Vinaphone 2018, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u00fa h\u00edch \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo th\u00eam t\u1ef1 tin b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o ASIAD. \u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 Olympic Pakistan, Nepal v\u00e0 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2110","checkdouble":"193980"},{"date":"01:04 08/08","title":"\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vui h\u1ebft n\u1ea5c khi n\u00e2ng c\u00fap, th\u1ea7y Park l\u1eb7ng l\u1ebd m\u1ed9t g\u00f3c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/8/nhung-hinh-anh-an-tuong-trong-ngay-dt-olympic-viet-nam-vo-dich-giai-tu-hung.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo vui h\u1ebft n\u1ea5c trong ng\u00e0y \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf v\u1edbi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">