.D (TTVN)</strong></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2109","checkdouble":"193981"},{"date":"05:51 08/08","title":"N\u00f3ng: Chelsea \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/29/chelsea-dong-y-chi-71-trieu-bang-mua-kepa-arrizabalaga.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd chi 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Kepa Arrizabalaga. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n b\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n tr\u1ebb n\u00e0y v\u1edbi Athletic Bilbao.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea kh\u00e1t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nghi ng\u1edd g\u00ec v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c Thibaut Courtois mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi b\u1ecf Chelsea v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1eddi m\u1eddi ch\u00e0o t\u1eeb Real Madrid, tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 ra \u0111i. T\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Chelsea \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd v\u1edbi Real b\u1ea5t th\u00e0nh, anh s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng bi\u1ec7n ph\u00e1p c\u1ee9ng r\u1eafn h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, \u0111\u00e3 2 ng\u00e0y tr\u00f4i qua k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb h\u1ea1n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n, Courtois v\u1eabn b\u1eb7t v\u00f4 \u00e2m t\u00edn. K\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m r\u00f5 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a HLV Maurizio Sarri c\u0169ng b\u1ecb h\u1ee7y b\u1ecf. Th\u00f4ng qua \u0111\u00f3, Courtois g\u1eedi \u0111i th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n mu\u1ed1n t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00eam b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 l\u1ea7n n\u00e0o cho Chelsea.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd chi 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Kepa Arrizabalaga h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd chi 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Kepa Arrizabalaga h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/15/Chelsea-dong-y-chi-71-trieu-bang-mua-Kepa-Arrizabalaga-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Courtois kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n thi\u1ebft tha \u1edf l\u1ea1i Real</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nChelsea \u0111\u00e3 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u Courtois b\u1eaft bu\u1ed9c ra tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m r\u00f5 v\u1ee5 vi\u1ec7c. H\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n duy tr\u00ec k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt trong \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng dung t\u00fang h\u00e0nh vi n\u00e0y. Song song v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, The Blues c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ea9y nhanh qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh t\u00ecm th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nCh\u1ed1t mua Kepa</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo th\u00f4ng tin m\u00e0 t\u1edd Telegraph m\u1edbi \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i, Chelsea \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd chi 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Kepa Arrizabalaga c\u1ee7a Athletic Bilbao. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Bilbao tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb n\u00e0o cho th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y 24 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi The Blues bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a anh n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfp di\u1ec5n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kepa Arrizabalaga\" title=\"Kepa Arrizabalaga\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/29/chelsea-dong-y-chi-71-trieu-bang-mua-kepa-arrizabalaga.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Chelsea \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd chi 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Kepa Arrizabalaga</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i n\u00e0y cho th\u1ea5y Chelsea s\u1eafp ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a CLB ch\u1ec9 sau 1 n\u0103m khi \u0111\u01b0a Alvaro Morata v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb Real Madrid v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 tr\u1ea3 ngay 58 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u0103ng l\u00ean 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u00f9y th\u00e0nh t\u00edch. N\u00f3 c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0a Kepa tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y 1 th\u00e1ng sau khi Liverpool chi 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Alisson t\u1eeb Roma.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u00fac n\u00e0y, Chelsea \u0111ang ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n c\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u1edbi Kepa. Song song v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng k\u1ef3 k\u00e8o Real gia t\u0103ng th\u00eam s\u1ee9c n\u1eb7ng trong \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb mua Courtois. Los Blancos ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n chi 31 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng (35 tri\u1ec7u Euro) trong khi CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n nh\u1eadn v\u1ec1 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/sevilla-muon-co-batshuayi-180-193959.html\">\u201cBom x\u1ecbt\u201d Chelsea s\u1eafp chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi La Liga thi \u0111\u1ea5u</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-muon-muon-kovacic-172-193958.html\">L\u1ed9 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ea7y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd c\u1ee7a Mateo Kovacic \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sao-chelsea-hy-vong-sarri-khong-kho-hieu-nhu-conte-172-193918.html\">Sao Chelsea hy v\u1ecdng Sarri kh\u00f4ng kh\u00f3 hi\u1ec3u nh\u01b0 Conte</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-cho-nantes-muon-matt-miazga-172-193916.html\">Sao tr\u1ebb Chelsea ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111em cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/barkley-phat-bieu-ve-tuong-lai-tai-chelsea-172-193912.html\">\u201cSao x\u1ecbt\u201d Chelsea hy v\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111\u1eddi d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Sarri</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2108","checkdouble":"193984"},{"date":"06:05 08/08","title":"V\u00f4 k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt, Courtois b\u1ecb Chelsea \u201cl\u00f4i c\u1ed5\u201d ra ph\u1ea1t","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/11/22/vo-ky-luat-courtois-bi-chelsea-loi-co-ra-phat.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Thibaut Courtois chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t t\u1eeb Chelsea. Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i trong 2 ng\u00e0y qua v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o The Blues kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ng\u1ed3i y\u00ean.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Courtois quy\u1ebft r\u1eddi Chelsea</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Thibaut Courtois v\u1edbi Chelsea ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m n\u1eefa l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1o h\u1ea1n. D\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 m\u1edf nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n su\u1ed1t m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i, The Blues v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 h\u1ee3p t\u00e1c c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u00e0y. Kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t gi\u1eefa m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 Courtois y\u00eau c\u1ea7u so v\u1edbi \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng c\u1ee7a Chelsea l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00ec th\u1ebf, Courtois quy\u1ebft r\u1eddi Chelsea trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Kh\u00f4ng thi\u1ebfu nh\u1eefng l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn d\u00e0nh cho tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 B\u1ec9. S\u1ed1t s\u1eafng nh\u1ea5t trong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i theo \u0111u\u1ed5i anh ph\u1ea3i k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn Real Madrid, nh\u1eefng nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League 3 n\u0103m li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thibaut Courtois chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t t\u1eeb Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Thibaut Courtois chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t t\u1eeb Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/Thibaut-Courtois-chuan-bi-nhan-an-phat-tu-Chelsea-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Courtois chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t t\u1eeb Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ebfn Real, Courtois kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i g\u00e2y \u00e1p l\u1ef1c cho Chelsea. Sau khi th\u00f4ng qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n y\u00eau c\u1ea7u CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n ch\u1ea5p thu\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Real b\u1ea5t th\u00e0nh, anh l\u1ea1i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111i m\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd h\u01a1n n\u1eefa. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, \u0111\u00e3 2 bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp qua, d\u00f9 h\u1ebft h\u1ea1n ngh\u1ec9 ph\u00e9p, Courtois v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp trung c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i. HLV Maurizio Sarri r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n g\u1eb7p g\u1ee1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00e0n b\u1ea1c v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai song kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u01b0 mong \u0111\u1ee3i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Chelsea v\u1eeba ra ch\u1ec9 th\u1ecb Thibaut Courtois bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i tham d\u1ef1 m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp v\u00e0o gi\u1edd \u0103n tr\u01b0a th\u1ee9 4 n\u00e0y. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111i k\u00e8m v\u1edbi Courtois chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t t\u1eeb Chelsea, v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n ph\u1ea1t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00ean t\u1edbi 2 tu\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thibaut Courtois noi ve tuong lai\" title=\"Thibaut Courtois n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/20/Nong-HLV-Real-bat-ngo-che-Thibaut-Courtois-hinh-anh.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 quy\u1ebft r\u1eddi Chelsea t\u1edbi Real</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00fang l\u00e0 Courtois \u0111\u00e3 th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o v\u1edbi HLV Sarri r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi Chelsea v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n ngh\u1ec9 t\u1eadp cho t\u1edbi khi t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai s\u00e1ng t\u1ecf. Song nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh 26 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c thay th\u1ebf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nChelsea \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau cho khung g\u1ed7 trong th\u1eddi gian qua. Sau c\u00f9ng, l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd ch\u1ed1t mua Kepa Arrizabalaga c\u1ee7a Athletic Bilbao. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chelsea-dong-y-chi-71-trieu-bang-mua-kepa-arrizabalaga-172-193984.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Kepa</span> tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n Courtois, m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 31 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 Real \u0111\u1eb7t ra cho Courtois ch\u01b0a khi\u1ebfn Chelsea h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00f2i 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u1edbi ch\u1ecbu nh\u1ea3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 13 trong \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t tr\u1eafng anh 