ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y cho t\u1edbi khi h\u1ecd t\u00ecm ra ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 B\u1ec9.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Tottenham ch\u1ea5p thu\u1eadn nh\u1ea3 Alderweireld cho M.U</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a HLV Jose Mourinho m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a M.U. \u00d4ng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ea5p tr\u00ean mang v\u1ec1 1 trong 2 c\u00e1i t\u00ean (ho\u1eb7c c\u1ea3 hai) Toby Alderweireld c\u1ee7a Tottenham v\u00e0 Harry Maguire.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1eb7t l\u00ean b\u00e0n c\u00e2n, th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Alderweireld l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 thi h\u01a1n v\u1edbi M.U. X\u00e9t v\u1ec1 t\u1ea7m quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi CLB, anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Maguire v\u1edbi Leicester City. C\u0169ng v\u00ec th\u1ebf, Leicester quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t ra \u0111i b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u00f3 s\u1ee9c n\u1eb7ng t\u1eeb M.U.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tottenham \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd b\u00e1n Toby Alderweireld cho MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tottenham \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd b\u00e1n Toby Alderweireld cho MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/3/Tin-chuyen-nhuong-hom-nay-ngay-48,-tin-chuyen-nhuong-he-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Tottenham \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd b\u00e1n Toby Alderweireld cho M.U</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 theo nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, Tottenham \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd b\u00e1n Toby Alderweireld cho M.U v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 75 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh qu\u1ea3 m\u00e0 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c sau khi theo \u0111u\u1ed5i trung v\u1ec7 29 tu\u1ed5i trong m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Tottenham</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng Tottenham kh\u00f4ng nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1ea1i Alderweireld cho M.U ngay b\u00e2y gi\u1edd. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 mang v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 thay th\u1ebf cho tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 B\u1ec9 trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Pochettino\" title=\"HLV Pochettino\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/Mauricio-Pochettino-noi-ve-chuyen-nhuong-Tottenham-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">HLV Pochettino ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 th\u00eam t\u00e2n binh n\u00e0o</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, Tottenham v\u1eabn \u0111ang g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c mua s\u1eafm. H\u1ecd nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i c\u00e1i t\u00ean nh\u01b0ng ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ai v\u1ec1. S\u1ef1 ch\u1eadm ch\u1ea1p trong tuy\u1ec3n m\u1ed9 nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Spurs l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u M.U l\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u01b0\u1edbc. H\u1ecd c\u0169ng chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb s\u1eb5n nh\u1eefng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n B n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c kh\u00f4ng t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ebf ch\u1ed7 Alderweireld.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, t\u1eeb gi\u1edd t\u1edbi khi k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00eam th\u1ee9 5 (9/8), M.U s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng mang v\u1ec1 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 1 trung v\u1ec7. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0 Alderweireld, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd li\u00ean h\u1ec7 g\u1ea5p v\u1edbi Yerry Mina c\u1ee7a Barcelona hay Jerome Boateng c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich v\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00e0 Maguire v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb n\u1eb7ng \u0111\u00f4.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 Alderweireld hay b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 c\u00e1i t\u00ean n\u00e0o \u1edf tr\u00ean gia nh\u1eadp, M.U c\u0169ng chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb s\u1eb5n tinh th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea9y \u0111i Marcos Rojo. H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina n\u1eb1m trong danh s\u00e1ch c\u1ea7n tinh gi\u1ea3n bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf m\u00e0 HLV Mourinho tr\u00ecnh l\u00ean l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng M.U tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/quan-diem-mu-nen-mua-zaha-172-193931.html\">Quan \u0111i\u1ec3m: M.U n\u00ean g\u1ea1t b\u1ecf s\u0129 di\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 mua l\u1ea1i Wilfried Zaha</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-dau-hieu-cuc-lon-cho-thay-mu-chuan-bi-don-trung-ve-moi-172-193882.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! D\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn cho th\u1ea5y M.U chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u00f3n trung v\u1ec7 m\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-pogba-da-tro-lai-man-united-172-193880.html\">Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c: Pogba \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Man United</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/willian-chinh-thuc-dua-ra-cau-tra-loi-cho-mu-barca-172-193877.html\">Willian ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0a ra c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho M.U, Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-gia-nhap-cuoc-dua-gianh-boateng-voi-mu-172-193871.html\">Arsenal gia nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh sao tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1edbi M.U</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/willian-mot-lan-nua-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-172-193826.html\">Willian: T\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 r\u1eddi Chelsea \u0111\u1ebfn MU ho\u1eb7c Real n\u1ebfu...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2105","checkdouble":"193988"},{"date":"06:49 08/08","title":"2 \u201ch\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i\u201d ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n t\u1edbi c\u00e1nh c\u1eeda r\u1eddi Arsenal","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/5/12/2-hang-thai-tien-gan-toi-canh-cua-roi-arsenal.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Arsenal s\u1eafp \u0111\u1ea9y \u0111i Lucas Perez v\u00e0 David Ospina. Trong khi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u1ebfn West Ham ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf th\u00ec th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Besiktas.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Perez s\u1eafp \u0111\u1ebfn West Ham</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 2 n\u0103m, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n 17 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Lucas Perez t\u1eeb Deportivo. Khi \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd m\u1edbi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Jamie Vardy v\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt l\u00e0 Perez \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u00e0n tr\u1ec1. Anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 th\u00edch nghi v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh gi\u00e0u th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 l\u00fac n\u00e0o c\u0169ng trong t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng \u0111u\u1ed1i s\u1ee9c. \u0110\u1ebfn m\u00f9a 2017/18, Perez b\u1ecb Arsenal \u0111\u1ea9y tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Deportivo d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n khi h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 Alexandre Lacazette.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Arsenal s\u1eafp \u0111\u1ea9y \u0111i Lucas Perez v\u00e0 David Ospina h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Arsenal s\u1eafp \u0111\u1ea9y \u0111i Lucas Perez v\u00e0 David Ospina h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/12/ban-hop-dong-thu-9-cua-west-ham-den-tu-arsenal.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Arsenal s\u1eafp \u0111\u1ea9y \u0111i Lucas Perez v\u00e0 David Ospina</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSang m\u00f9a m\u1edbi 2018/19, Perez ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ee9ng trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Arsenal. Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 cho m\u00ecnh nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn kh\u00e1c \u1edf hai c\u00e1nh c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung phong v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch c\u1ea7n thanh l\u00fd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau khi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb 9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb West Ham, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd, ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn l\u1ed7 8 tri\u1ec7u t\u1eeb Perez sau 2 n\u0103m. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ebfn ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf t\u1ea1i West Ham v\u00e0 s\u1edbm ra m\u1eaft CLB n\u00e0y. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"thu mon Ospina\" title=\"thu mon Ospina\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/2/15/hlv-wenger-xac-nhan-thu-mon-bat-chinh-truoc-man-city.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ospina \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Besiktas</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nOspina \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Besiktas</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 Lucas Perez, David Ospina kh\u00f4ng kh\u00e1c g\u00ec &ldquo;ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1eeba&rdquo; c\u1ee7a Arsenal trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c mang v\u1ec1 Bernd Leno t\u1eeb Bayer Leverkusen c\u1ed9ng th\u00eam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1eb5n Petr Cech, Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u1ea7n th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia d\u00f9 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u00f3ng b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c Ospina chia tay Arsenal h\u00e8 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Theo nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, anh \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Besiktas v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 \u0111ang c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n m\u1edbi thay th\u1ebf Tolga Zengin s\u1eafp sang tu\u1ed5i 35. Ospina tr\u1ebb h\u01a1n 4 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p nhi\u1ec1u cho Besiktas.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Arsenal tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-gia-nhap-cuoc-dua-gianh-boateng-voi-mu-172-193871.html\">Arsenal gia nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh sao tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1edbi M.U</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-bao-tin-buon-cho-arsenal-vu-dembele-180-193861.html\">Barca b\u00e1o tin bu\u1ed3n cho Arsenal v\u1ee5 bom t\u1ea5n 105 tri\u1ec7u euro</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/xac-nhan-arsenal-va-chelsea-quan-tam-leon-bailey-172-193859.html\">X\u00e1c nh\u1eadn: Arsenal v\u00e0 Chelsea quan t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng hot Bundesliga</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-nham-sao-thuy-sy-thay-nacho-monreal-172-193853.html\">Arsenal nh\u1eafm sao Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 thay Nacho Monreal</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/aaron-ramsey-phu-nhan-voi-vinh-arsenal-bang-luong-khung-172-193837.html\">Aaron Ramsey ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn v\u00f2i v\u0129nh Arsenal b\u1eb1ng l\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u1ee7ng</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2104","checkdouble":"193989"},{"date":"15:22 07/08","title":"S\u1ed1 4 v\u00e0 c\u01a1n \u0111au \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y Park","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/so-4-va-con-dau-dau-cua-thay-park.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo lu\u1eadt ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i ASIAD, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 qu\u00e1 \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i U23. V\u00e0 HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i lo\u1ea1i ai trong s\u1ed1 4 c\u1ef1u binh c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam?</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-uzbekistan-tran-dau-ngay-hom-nay-78-372-193948.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-uzbekistan-tran-dau-ngay-hom-nay-78.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-uzbekistan-tran-dau-ngay-hom-nay-78-372-193948.html\">TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Uzbekistan 19h30 ng\u00e0y 7/8 (U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf 2018)</span><br>\r\n<span>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Uzbekistan: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 k\u00e8m link xem tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\nC\u01a1n \u0111au \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y Park</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng \u00edt ng\u01b0\u1eddi lu\u00f4n e ng\u1ea1i con s\u1ed1 4 b\u1edfi theo quan ni\u1ec7m ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0110\u00f4ng, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 con s\u1ed1 t\u1eed. V\u00e0 v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y Park, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u00f4ng c\u0169ng \u0111ang r\u1ea5t \u0111au \u0111\u1ea7u khi s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec3 ai v\u00e0o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ed1 4 trong 4 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i 23 l\u00fac n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1edbi n\u00f2ng c\u1ed1t l\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U23 v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a 4 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean tu\u1ed5i 23 \u0111ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang Indonesia tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"S\u1ed1 4 v\u00e0 c\u01a1n \u0111au \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"S\u1ed1 4 v\u00e0 c\u01a1n \u0111au \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/hlv-park-hang-seo-gui-loi-nhan-toi-nguoi-ham-mo-bong-da-viet-nam.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i g\u1ea1ch t\u00ean m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i 23 khi ch\u1ed1t danh s\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ed1i nay, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi U23 Uzbekistan, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1ebd ch\u1ecdn ra nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng HLV Park Hang Seo tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i \u00e1p l\u1ef1c c\u1ea1nh tranh l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111ang r\u1ea5t n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam b\u1edfi h\u1ecd r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 &lsquo;ghi \u0111i\u1ec3m&rsquo; trong m\u1eaft \u00f4ng Park. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb m\u00e0, nh\u1eefng &lsquo;l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng&rsquo; c\u0169ng \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh V\u0103n L\u00e2m \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 su\u1ea5t b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u00ec c\u1ea3 Anh \u0110\u1ee9c, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft, H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc su\u1ea5t \u1edf l\u1ea1i. V\u00e0 v\u00ec th\u1ebf, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi v\u1edbi Uzbekistan \u0111\u1ec3 qua \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00ecnh x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/u23-viet-nam-vo-dich-vinaphone-cup-loi-khang-dinh-cua-thay-park-168-193817.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/u23-viet-nam-vo-dich-vinaphone-cup-loi-khang-dinh-cua-thay-park.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/u23-viet-nam-vo-dich-vinaphone-cup-loi-khang-dinh-cua-thay-park-168-193817.html\">U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf: L\u1eddi kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y Park</span><br>\r\nTh\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u00e0 kinh nghi\u1ec7m trong ngh\u1ec1 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi gi\u00fap  U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Vinaphone Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110i t\u00ecm s\u1ed1 4<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u0169ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t n\u0103m c\u00f3 4 m\u00f9a xu\u00e2n, h\u1ea1, thu, \u0111\u00f4ng th\u00ec trong tay HLV Park Hang Seo l\u00fac n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111ang c\u00f3 4 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean 23 tu\u1ed5i xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c b\u1ed5 sung v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 ASIAD.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 c\u0169ng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 m\u00f9a \u0110\u00f4ng lu\u00f4n \u0111\u1ebfn sau c\u00f9ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n b\u1edfi s\u1ef1 l\u1ea1nh l\u1ebdo, t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a n\u00f3 th\u00ec ch\u1eafc h\u1eb3n 4 h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng Park c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng mong mu\u1ed1n m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd r\u01a1i v\u00e0o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ed1 4, v\u1ecb tr\u00ed t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i \u1edf nh\u00e0 xem ASIAD. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean quy \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1eabn l\u00e0 quy \u0111\u1ecbnh, v\u00e0 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn lu\u1eadt ch\u01a1i chung l\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i 23 khi tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Park Hang Seo t\u1eebng n\u00f3i s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng 3 'c\u1ef1u binh' \u1edf ASIAD 2018, v\u00e0 l\u00fac n\u00e0y, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u1eabn \u0111ang chia \u0111\u1ec1u cho c\u1ea3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Anh \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 hai ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i l\u00e0 V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft v\u00e0 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Olympic Viet Nam\" title=\"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/vq-01-1640.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Li\u1ec7u V\u0103n L\u00e2m, Anh \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft s\u1ebd l\u00e0 3 'c\u1ef1u binh' tr\u1ee5 l\u1ea1i \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam?</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Anh \u0110\u1ee9c d\u00f9 l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ed1 1 tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam nh\u01b0ng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 tu\u1ed5i t\u00e1c l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i cho anh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tu\u1ed5i 33, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng Anh \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd v\u00e0 nhanh nh\u1eb9n nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Do \u0111\u00f3 n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea9n th\u1eadn ho\u1eb7c d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd b\u1ecb thay th\u1ebf b\u1edfi c\u00e1c trung phong tr\u1ebb trung kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh hay Nguy\u1ec5n Ti\u1ebfn Linh.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft d\u00f9 n\u1eafm gi\u1eef t\u1ea5m b\u0103ng th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ed1t \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Uzbekistan, anh c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u1eabn b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 \u00edt nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103ng n\u1ed5 nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 c\u00f2n nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi khen t\u1eeb c\u1ea3 hai HLV U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Palestine, tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1eabn c\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng \u00edt \u00fd ki\u1ebfn cho r\u1eb1ng s\u1ef1 ch\u1eadm ch\u1ea1p v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n sai v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Quy\u1ebft &lsquo;c\u00f2i&rsquo; l\u1ea1i v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh l\u00e0m gi\u1ea3m c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-uzbekistan-19h30-ngay-078-doi-no-duoc-khong-168-193900.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/nhan-dinh-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-uzbekistan-19h30-ngay-078-doi-no-duoc-khong.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-uzbekistan-19h30-ngay-078-doi-no-duoc-khong-168-193900.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Uzbekistan (19h30 ng\u00e0y 07/8): \u0110\u00f2i n\u1ee3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00f4ng?</span><br>\r\nU23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00f2i n\u1ee3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc U23 Uzbekistan sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018. V\u00e0 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo \u0111ang c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf \u1edf...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng, d\u00f9 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ebfn sau nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng \u0111ang r\u1ea5t n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm hy v\u1ecdng tr\u1ee5 l\u1ea1i. Vi\u1ec7c \u00f4ng Park s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 gi\u1eef 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111ang khi\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i d\u00f9 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a anh \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 2 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u0111\u00e1ng khen ng\u1ee3i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Olympic Oman. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed anh c\u00f2n su\u00fdt n\u1eefa \u0111i\u1ec1n t\u00ean m\u00ecnh l\u00ean b\u1ea3ng \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed n\u1ebfu th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00f4ng xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 c\u00fa s\u00fat c\u1ee7a anh \u1edf ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 82.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Do Hung Dung\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/tien-ve-hung-dung-lo-lang-ve-kha-nang-du-asiad.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, nh\u00ecn nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch t\u1ed5ng th\u1ec3 th\u00ec D\u0169ng &lsquo;ch\u00edp&rsquo; kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m so v\u1edbi c\u00e1c '\u0111\u00e0n em' U23, trong khi kinh nghi\u1ec7m thi \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1eb1ng V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft, Anh \u0110\u1ee9c hay V\u0103n L\u00e2m, n\u00ean n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 anh b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i th\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i t\u00f3m l\u1ea1i, Anh \u0110\u1ee9c, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft v\u00e0 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea5u tay 3 \u1edf tr\u1eadn U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Uzbekistan t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e2n \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1eafng, b\u1ea1i. Theo nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin, r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 3 \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh. \u0110\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 d\u1ecbp \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng nh\u1ea5t v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ra s\u1ed1 4 m\u00e0 m\u00ecnh \u0111ang c\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Highlight Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Palestine<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">\t</span></strong></p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/3/Highlight-Viet-Nam-vs-Palestine-.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/danh-sach-chinh-thuc-dt-olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-ai-se-bi-loai-168-193940.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/danh-sach-chinh-thuc-dt-olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-ai-se-bi-loai.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/danh-sach-chinh-thuc-dt-olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-ai-se-bi-loai-168-193940.html\">Danh s\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 ASIAD: Ai s\u1ebd b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i?</span><br>\r\nSau khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Uzbekistan k\u1ebft th\u00fac, HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0a ra danh s\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 ASIAD. V\u00e0 li\u1ec7u ai s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ecdn...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/lo-dien-doi-hinh-ra-san-tran-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-uzbekistan-168-193938.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/lo-dien-doi-hinh-ra-san-tran-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-uzbekistan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/lo-dien-doi-hinh-ra-san-tran-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-uzbekistan-168-193938.html\">L\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ra s\u00e2n tr\u1eadn U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Uzbekistan</span><br>\r\nTheo ngu\u1ed3n tin th\u00e2n c\u1eadn, g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd tung ra \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Uzbekistan v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i nay 7/8.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2103","checkdouble":"193944"},{"date":"15:59 07/08","title":"Ferdinand \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi khuy\u00ean chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho MU","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/ferdinand-len-tieng-canh-bao-man-united.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Rio Ferdinand v\u1eeba l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u CEO Ed Woodward d\u1eb9p tan nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn Pogba v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a Alderweireld v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Old Trafford ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c.</h2><h2>T\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf MU</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Man United m\u1edbi chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd l\u00e0 Fred t\u1eeb Shakhtar v\u00e0 Diogo Dalot t\u1eeb Porto. Ch\u1eebng \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1ecfa l\u1ea5p nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Mourinho t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Man United. \u00d4ng c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y \u00e1p l\u1ef1c l\u00ean Ed Woodward khi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u \u0111\u1ea7y \u1ea9n \u00fd sau tr\u1eadn thua Bayern Munich h\u00f4m Ch\u1ee7 nh\u1eadt. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Mourinho cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ea7n b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Rio Ferdinand \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi khuy\u00ean chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Rio Ferdinand \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi khuy\u00ean chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/ferdinand-len-tieng-canh-bao-man-united.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Ferdinand \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khuy\u00ean chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho Ed Woodward</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Man United \u0111ang theo \u0111u\u1ed5i trung v\u1ec7 Toby Alderweireld c\u1ee7a Tottenham v\u00e0 \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u1ea1n ch\u00f3t chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 N\u0103m t\u1edbi. T\u1edd Goal cho bi\u1ebft Alderweireld \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd gia nh\u1eadp MU nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn \u0111ang ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Willian c\u1ee7a Chelsea c\u0169ng m\u1edbi b\u00e0y t\u1ecf mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c c\u00f9ng Mourinho m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa. Nh\u01b0ng ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a The Blues c\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn Old Trafford ngay \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede chi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, Man United c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111ang \u1edf trong cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn nh\u1eb1m gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Pogba kh\u1ecfi t\u1ea7m v\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Barcelona. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u01b0a Andre Silva v\u00e0 Yerry Mina t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Old Trafford k\u00e8m theo 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Nh\u01b0ng Man United kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y m\u1eb7n m\u00e0 trong vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ec3 Pogba ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n<h2>Ferdinand l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng khuy\u00ean nh\u1ee7 Ed Woodward</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111ang bao quanh Man United hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Ferdinand \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khuy\u00ean cho CEO Ed Woodward tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda. Chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean Twitter c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, Ferdinand l\u1edbn ti\u1ebfng:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201c\u00d4ng d\u00e1m \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y x\u1ea3y ra h\u1ea3 Ed? Man United l\u00e0 nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a Pogba. D\u1eadp t\u1eaft ngay nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n n\u00e0y v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a Alderweireld v\u1ec1 nhanh l\u00ean\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Man United:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/phil-jones-ha-quyet-tam-gianh-suat-da-chinh-o-mu-172-193930.html\">Phil Jones h\u1ea1 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u00e0nh su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf MU</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-0708-them-mot-cau-thu-chinh-thuc-chia-tay-mu-184-193907.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 07/08: Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C chia tay MU</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2102","checkdouble":"193947"},{"date":"15:42 07/08","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Uzbekistan 19h30 ng\u00e0y 7/8 (U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-uzbekistan-tran-dau-ngay-hom-nay-78.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i Quang H\u1ea3i ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0. B\u1edfi v\u1edbi c\u00e1i ch\u00e2n tr\u00e1i r\u1ea5t d\u1ecb c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f9ng U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u00e1 qu\u00e2n ch\u00e2u \u00c1. V\u00e0 t\u1ed1i nay nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169ng \u0111ang k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng ch\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng.</h2><p>\u00a0</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-uzbekistan-tran-dau-ngay-hom-nay-78-372-193948.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-uzbekistan-tran-dau-ngay-hom-nay-78.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-uzbekistan-tran-dau-ngay-hom-nay-78-372-193948.html\">TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Uzbekistan 19h30 ng\u00e0y 7/8 (U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf 2018)</span><br>\r\nTr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Uzbekistan: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 k\u00e8m link xem tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Khi b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u00e3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 1 v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n Quang H\u1ea3i khi \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i c\u0169ng l\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1eddi trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00fa s\u00fat \u1edf kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch g\u1ea7n 30m so v\u1edbi khung th\u00e0nh U23 Uzbekistan \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Quang H\u1ea3i th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o. B\u00f3ng \u0111i xo\u00e1y v\u1edbi qu\u1ef9 \u0111\u1ea1o kh\u00e1 hi\u1ec3m h\u00f3c v\u00e0o g\u00f3c ch\u1eef A \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n U23 Uzbekistan d\u00f9 c\u00f3 bay ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ebft c\u1ee1 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n b\u00f3ng \u0111i v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam Ch\u1edd m\u1ed9t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng cong c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam Ch\u1edd m\u1ed9t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng cong c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/photo1517043181499-1517043181499799305547.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>NHM \u0111ang r\u1ea5t ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i Quang H\u1ea3i l\u1eadp si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m \u1edf tr\u1eadn t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa\u00a0</em><i>U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Uzbekistan</i></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pha s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t m\u1eabu m\u1ef1c \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam k\u00e9o d\u00e0i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 120 v\u00e0 c\u00f3 l\u00fac \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n v\u1edbi vinh quang, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ebfn m\u1ed9 nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t trong l\u00f2ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Uzbekistan v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i nay, c\u0169ng \u0111ang c\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng \u00edt ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1eabn \u0111ang mong Quang H\u1ea3i s\u1ebd l\u1eadp l\u1ea1i si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m khi t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Trung \u00c1 nhi\u1ec1u duy\u00ean n\u1ee3, v\u00e0 mang v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Uzbekistan, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 Quang H\u1ea3i m\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 d\u1ecbp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00f2i m\u00f3n n\u1ee3 c\u0169, cho d\u00f9 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec. D\u1eabu sao m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1eebng gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ch\u00e2u \u00c1 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ngu\u1ed3n c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo t\u1ef1 tin b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o chinh ph\u1ee5c ASIAD.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00fac n\u00e0y, b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n thay \u0111\u1ed5i khi U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng mang theo l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t. Do \u0111\u00f3, U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u00f2n Quang H\u1ea3i c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd t\u00e1i l\u1eadp si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m \u2018c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng Tuy\u1ebft\u2019 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/so-4-va-con-dau-dau-cua-thay-park-168-193944.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/so-4-va-con-dau-dau-cua-thay-park.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/so-4-va-con-dau-dau-cua-thay-park-168-193944.html\">S\u1ed1 4 v\u00e0 c\u01a1n \u0111au \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y Park</span><br>\r\nTheo lu\u1eadt ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i ASIAD, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 qu\u00e1 \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i U23. V\u00e0 HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i lo\u1ea1i ai trong s\u1ed1 4 c\u1ef1u binh c\u1ee7a Olympic...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1eabn \u0111ang c\u00f2n thi\u1ebfu b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Quang H\u1ea3i<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu Vinaphone Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y sau hai chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp tr\u01b0\u1edbc Palestine v\u00e0 Oman. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i, c\u1ea3 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u00e0 c\u00e1c chi\u1ebfn binh \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trong c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u00fa s\u00fat \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Anh \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1edbi t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t pha ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft, b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng mang \u0111\u1eadm d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin c\u00f2n si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m mang phong c\u00e1ch trivela c\u1ee7a \u0110o\u00e0n V\u0103n H\u1eadu l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng ngo\u00e0i s\u1ef1 mong \u0111\u1ee3i th\u00ec ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 v\u1eabn \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng Quang H\u1ea3i s\u1ebd l\u1eadp si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i k\u1ebft m\u1ef9 m\u00e3n cho th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i Vinaphone Cup.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam Ch\u1edd m\u1ed9t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng cong c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam Ch\u1edd m\u1ed9t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng cong c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/U23-Viet-Nam-Cho-mot-duong-cong-cua-nguoi-dac-biet-hinh-anh-2.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f2n thi\u1ebfu b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Nguy\u1ec5n Quang H\u1ea3i \u1edf gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Quang H\u1ea3i \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n ch\u1ea1y n\u01b0\u1edbc r\u00fat c\u1ee7a V-League 2018, nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi tin r\u1eb1ng anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. 6 th\u00e1ng sau ng\u00e0y th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc U23 Uzbekistan t\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1, Quang H\u1ea3i l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111ang ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 h\u01a1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i V-League 2018, d\u00f9 c\u00f3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 \u00fd song Quang H\u1ea3i c\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1ea1i c\u00e0ng tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n qua t\u1eebng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 9 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 20 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i V-League 2018 l\u00e0 con s\u1ed1 cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 nguy hi\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 nh\u1ecf con n\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ecdi h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y nh\u1ea5t, anh ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t pha tung ch\u00e2n ngo\u00e0i v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m mang v\u1ec1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng qu\u00fd gi\u00e1 cho H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u1edf tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 3-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ea1i Cup Qu\u1ed1c gia 2018. Sau nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n, Quang H\u1ea3i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Uzbekistan t\u1ed1i nay.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, HLV Uzbekistan \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 Quang H\u1ea3i l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t nguy hi\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. V\u00e0 nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n n\u00e0y l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c b\u1edfi lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t Quang H\u1ea3i lu\u00f4n bi\u1ebft t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng khi U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/danh-sach-chinh-thuc-dt-olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-ai-se-bi-loai-168-193940.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/danh-sach-chinh-thuc-dt-olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-ai-se-bi-loai.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/danh-sach-chinh-thuc-dt-olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-ai-se-bi-loai-168-193940.html\">Danh s\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 ASIAD: Ai s\u1ebd b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i?</span><br>\r\nSau khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Uzbekistan k\u1ebft th\u00fac, HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0a ra danh s\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 ASIAD. V\u00e0 li\u1ec7u ai s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ecdn...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:\n115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2101","checkdouble":"193948"},{"date":"16:07 07/08","title":"Chelsea s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Courtois","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/chelsea-muon-mua-kepa-arrizabalaga.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Kepa Arrizabalaga c\u1ee7a Athletic Bilbao. H\u1ecd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 80 tri\u1ec7u Euro \u0111\u1ec3 mang th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u00e0y v\u1ec1 thay th\u1ebf Thibaut Courtois.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Courtois d\u1ee9t kho\u00e1t r\u1eddi Chelsea</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Thibaut Courtois v\u1edbi Chelsea ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m n\u1eefa l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1o h\u1ea1n. Sau khi nh\u1eefng th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn gia h\u1ea1n b\u1ea5t th\u00e0nh b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng kh\u00fac m\u1eafc v\u1ec1 l\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1ed5ng, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi Real Madrid. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 35 tri\u1ec7u Euro \u0111\u1ec3 mua l\u1ea1i h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 1 n\u0103m c\u1ee7a anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nReal s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ch\u1edd th\u00eam 12 th\u00e1ng n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3n Courtois v\u1ec1 d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 4 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n bao g\u1ed3m Keylor Navas, Kiko Casilla c\u1ed9ng th\u00eam 2 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb l\u00e0 Andriy Lunin v\u00e0 Luca Zidane. N\u1ebfu ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 Courtois, Los Blancos c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Kepa Arrizabalaga c\u1ee7a Athletic Bilbao h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Kepa Arrizabalaga c\u1ee7a Athletic Bilbao h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/Chelsea-muon-mua-Kepa-Arrizabalaga-cua-Athletic-Bilbao-hinh-anh.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Courtois mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Chelsea \u0111\u1ebfn Real</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, Courtois th\u00ec \u0111ang t\u1ecf ra s\u1ed1t ru\u1ed9t. Th\u00f4ng qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n, anh y\u00eau c\u1ea7u Chelsea ch\u1ea5p thu\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 h\u1ee3p l\u00fd c\u1ee7a Real. Tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 B\u1ec9 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a nh\u01b0 d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i t\u1ecf r\u00f5 l\u1eadp tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea t\u00ednh t\u1ea1o \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea th\u00ec d\u1ee9t kho\u00e1t ch\u1ec9 nh\u1ea3 Courtois n\u1ebfu t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf t\u1eeb gi\u1edd t\u1edbi l\u00fac th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00f3ng l\u1ea1i v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam th\u1ee9 5 t\u1edbi (9/8). Sau Jordan Pickford c\u1ee7a Everton hay Jack Butland c\u1ee7a Stoke, h\u1ecd nh\u1eafm Jan Oblak c\u1ee7a Atletico Madrid v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 89 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"thu mon Kepa\" title=\"thu mon Kepa\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/chelsea-muon-mua-kepa-arrizabalaga.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Kepa Arrizabalaga c\u1ee7a Bilbao</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Kepa Arrizabalaga c\u1ee7a Athletic Bilbao. C\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Oblak, The Blues s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi \u0111\u1eadm \u201cx\u00e9\u201d h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Kepa v\u1edbi CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra l\u00ean t\u1edbi 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng (80 tri\u1ec7u Euro).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2018, su\u00fdt n\u1eefa Kepa \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Real Madrid. C\u00e1c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c b\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng qua song b\u1ecb h\u1ee7y b\u1ecf b\u1edfi s\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng Zinedine Zidane. Sau \u0111\u00f3, Kepa \u1edf l\u1ea1i Bilbao v\u00e0 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Basque.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-cho-nantes-muon-matt-miazga-172-193916.html\">Sao tr\u1ebb Chelsea ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111em cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/khung-khiep-chelsea-chi-89-trieu-bang-cho-nguoi-thay-the-courtois-172-193897.html\">Kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp: Chelsea chi 89 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Courtois</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/courtois-tu-choi-tro-lai-chelsea-quyet-tam-den-real-bang-duoc-172-193892.html\">Courtois t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn Real b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sao-chelsea-courtois-va-hazard-cu-thoai-mai-ra-di-172-193879.html\">Sao Chelsea: \u201cCourtois v\u00e0 Hazard c\u1ee9 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i ra \u0111i\u201d</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tottenham-sap-co-tan-binh-voi-gia-18-trieu-bang-172-193870.html\">Tottenham mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Chelsea v\u1ee5 sao Aston Villa</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2100","checkdouble":"193949"},{"date":"16:39 07/08","title":"V\u00ec \u201cmi\u1ebfng b\u00e1nh\u201d b\u00e9o b\u1edf n\u00e0y, Modric t\u00ednh b\u1ecf Real sang Inter","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/luka-modric-tinh-roi-real-sang-inter-milan.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Luka Modric t\u00ednh r\u1eddi Real sang Inter Milan. Nh\u1eefng \u01b0u \u0111\u00e3i m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia d\u00e0nh cho ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 g\u1ea7n 33 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u01b0\u1ee1ng l\u1ea1i.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Inter d\u00f9ng \u201cm\u1ed3i ngon\u201d chi\u00eau d\u1ee5</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo th\u00f4ng tin m\u00e0 t\u1edd AS c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, Luka Modric t\u00ednh r\u1eddi Real sang Inter Milan. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi t\u1edbi tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Croatia nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd t\u0103ng g\u1ea7n g\u1ea5p \u0111\u00f4i ti\u1ec1n l\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Modric v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n cho anh chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 trong m\u01a1 sau khi h\u1ebft h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Inter \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb m\u1ed9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 4 n\u0103m v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00ean t\u1edbi 9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng (10 tri\u1ec7u Euro)/ n\u0103m cho Modric. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh th\u00e1ng 9 n\u0103m 1985 ch\u1ec9 ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 5,8 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng (6,5 tri\u1ec7u Euro) m\u1ed7i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1ea1i Real Madrid.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Luka Modric t\u00ednh r\u1eddi Real sang Inter Milan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Luka Modric t\u00ednh r\u1eddi Real sang Inter Milan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/luka-modric-tinh-roi-real-sang-inter-milan.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Inter d\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn thu h\u00fat Modric</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Modric v\u1edbi Real ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n hi\u1ec7u l\u1ef1c 2 n\u0103m. Anh s\u1ee3 r\u1eb1ng sau \u0111\u00f3 m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng kh\u00e1c. Vi\u1ec7c Inter \u0111\u01b0a ra m\u1ed9t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn t\u1edbi 4 n\u0103m, m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u0103ng \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn Modric bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i suy ngh\u0129.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u00eam n\u1eefa, Inter c\u0169ng h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u Modric sang Trung Qu\u1ed1c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng k\u1ebfch x\u00f9 sau khi h\u1ebft h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng. C\u00e1c \u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 Nerazzurri hi\u1ec7n ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1ef7 d\u00e2n v\u00e0 c\u00f3 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 r\u1ed9ng kh\u1eafp v\u1edbi c\u00e1c CLB t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Modric b\u1ecb ph\u00e2n t\u00e2m</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLuka Modric d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c g\u1eb7p l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Real Madrid khi CLB tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eeb chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9. D\u00f9 sao, n\u1ebfu Real kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0y, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 s\u1eafp 33 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Santiago Bernabeu.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Luka Modric\" title=\"Luka Modric\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/Luka-Modric.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Luka Modric t\u00ednh r\u1eddi Real sang Inter Milan</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1eeb khi gia nh\u1eadp Real t\u1eeb Tottenham v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2012, Modric \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 4 Champions League, 1 La Liga c\u00f9ng nhi\u1ec1u danh hi\u1ec7u kh\u00e1c. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a anh v\u1edbi Los Blancos l\u00ean t\u1edbi 670 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng (750 tri\u1ec7u Euro).<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus, Modric tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00e1n ra nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Real. Song khi m\u00e0 Inter Milan r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y khi h\u1ecd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Champions League l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u sau 6 n\u0103m, Modric v\u1eabn n\u1eb1m trong t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Inter \u0111\u00e3 mang v\u1ec1 7 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb h\u01a1n 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Inter Milan tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/inter-quyet-tam-chieu-mo-bang-duoc-luka-modric-176-193748.html\">Inter quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Luka Modric</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/them-mot-doi-bong-hoi-mua-hau-ve-mu-172-193679.html\">Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u1ecfi mua h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 MU</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/chinh-thuc-nguoi-hung-world-cup-se-doi-dau-ronaldo-o-y-184-192442.html\">Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c: Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng World Cup s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Ronaldo \u1edf \u00dd</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-ra-gia-modric-cho-cac-doi-tac-180-192606.html\">V\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n n\u00e0y, M.U v\u00e0 Inter c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mang Modric r\u1eddi Real</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/hlv-spalletti-phat-bieu-ve-chuyen-nhuong-inter-176-192251.html\">HLV Inter Milan mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 th\u00eam c\u00e1c t\u00e2n binh</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2099","checkdouble":"193950"}]}